Class BulkAdGroupLocationCriterion

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.microsoft.bingads.v12.internal.bulk.BulkObject
      • com.microsoft.bingads.v12.bulk.entities.BulkEntity
        • com.microsoft.bingads.v12.internal.bulk.entities.SingleRecordBulkEntity
          • com.microsoft.bingads.v12.bulk.entities.BulkAdGroupLocationCriterion

  • public class BulkAdGroupLocationCriterion
extends SingleRecordBulkEntity
    Represents a location criterion that is assigned to an ad group. Each location criterion can be read or written in a bulk file.

    For more information, see Ad Group Location Criterion at See Also:

    BulkServiceManager, BulkOperation, BulkFileReader, BulkFileWriter
